 yes, <TIMEX2 val="PRESENT_REF" mod="" set="" non_specific="" anchor_val="2000-10-19T18:32:34.15" anchor_dir="AS_OF" comment="">current</TIMEX2> administration has presided over <TIMEX2 val="PXY" mod="" set="" non_specific="" anchor_val="2000" anchor_dir="ENDING" comment="">years of prosperity</TIMEX2>, but bush
