<TURN>
 the economic growth of <TIMEX2 val="PRESENT_REF" mod="" set="" non_specific="" anchor_val="2000-10-19T18:32:34.15" anchor_dir="AS_OF" comment="">today</TIMEX2> has occurred because of ingenuity and hard work,
